1. install github cli

2. install act (gh extension install nektos/gh-act)

3. gh auth login (git token keresztul belep a githubra)

4. git init (csak elso alkalomman)

5. gh repo clone <repo name> (gh repo list - kimutassa)

6. cd <repo> (belepunk a repoba amit clonoltunk)

7. act (a repon belul futtasuk a github actiont)

8. git pull (frissiti a reponkat)

- delete repo: rm -fr <repo> 
